    <h2>Advantages</h2>
    <p>High natural strength; responds well to strength training. Suitable for strength and power-based activities.</p>

    <!-- Disadvantages Section -->
    <h2>Disadvantages</h2>
    <p>Needs careful calorie control due to a predisposition to gain fat. Lower carbohydrate tolerance than other body types.</p>

